{'docs': [{'title': 'IN$DEX Overview', 'content': 'IN$DEX is a decentralized exchange for creators to sell goods using crypto and fiat, without KYC. Users earn XP and mint NFTs tied to marketplace activity.'}, {'title': 'Marae Vault', 'content': 'The Marae Vault allows users to lock XP and receive NFT badge rewards weekly. It functions as a ceremonial reward chamber for top-performing creators.'}, {'title': 'Quests and Drops', 'content': 'IN$DEX offers smart quests and Legendary Drops where creators can earn special NFTs and ranking boosts through campaign tasks and community events.'}]}